works.description: Frederique Constant is a luxury wrist watches manufacturer based in Plan-les-Ouates Geneva. It has already made its mark in designing and producing some of the most magnificent watches for men like the one produced in 2010 along with General Cigar Company Inc. The company is now celebrating its 5th anniversary of its manufacturing unit in Geneva. To celebrate the occasion, the company has revealed details of three unique timepieces. The specialty this time is the women collection launched by the company for the first time
